## How Claude should use this file

When I mention a carrier name, look here for the contact, the renewal pattern, and the gotchas. When I am building a carrier comparison, draw from the "what they are good at" and "what to watch out for" sections. When I ask "who do I email at [carrier] for [product line]," surface the named contact and the last-known-good date. If I have not updated this file in over six months, surface that as a flag because the contacts are likely stale.
